ven the likes of this,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33902,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/09\/prohibition-divorcing-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":10955,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Talaq: Prohibition of divorcing women during menstruation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: He divorced his wife in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while she menstruating. Umar ibn al-Khattab asked the Prophet about that and he said, \u201cOrder him to return her. Let him leave her alone until she becomes pure, then\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/gabriel-emphasizes-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":10955,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Gabriel emphasizes good behavior to neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel did not stop instructing me to treat neighbors well until I thought he would make them my heirs.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6015, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2625 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0